1
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:44,960
Let him go.

2
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:57,690
His divine soul has been trapped in this body.

3
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,360
After 30 years of torment,

4
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,760
he can't hold on anymore.

5
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:02,760
He can't hold on?

6
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,599
He is about to dissipate.

7
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,000
However,

8
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:09,039
his life was extended by the current Child of the World.

9
00:01:09,039 --> 00:01:11,970
But it's just a drop in the bucket to force him to stay.

10
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:13,920
If you let him go now,

11
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:17,140
he might still have a chance to return to his origin.

12
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,600
Where is your demon core?

13
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:28,960
Guess.

14
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:30,880
Her demon core

15
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:33,100
is inside this Taoist priest's body.

16
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,979
How do you know?

17
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,800
Don't even think about hurting him.

18
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:39,160
Yueqi,

19
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,280
you've trapped him for so many years.

20
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:42,340
It's time to let go.

21
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,200
Let go?

22
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,280
No way.

23
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,880
He hasn't woken up yet.

24
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,479
His soul

25
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,039
is still in this body.

26
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,680
After so many years of wear and tear,

27
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,740
if you don't let go,

28
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,259
he will really dissipate.

29
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,940
You're lying to me.

30
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,890
You can't take him away.

31
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,280
Fairy Yueqi,

32
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,760
don't be stubborn

33
00:02:26,160 --> 00:02:27,360
and create more sins.

34
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,680
Cultivation is not easy for demons.

35
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,720
Life is hard.

36
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,040
I beg you two

37
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,520
to show mercy

38
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,180
and spare her life.

39
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,520
Little Flower Demon,

40
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,000
go quickly.

41
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:15,960
No.

42
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,720
No.

43
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,160
No.

44
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,240
No.

45
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,360
My hands are covered in blood.

46
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,360
I don't deserve you dying for me.

47
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,080
Daoist.

48
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,560
I only wish for you

49
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,680
to enter reincarnation

50
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,200
and be born human again.

51
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,120
Yue Qi...

52
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,600
She is using her demon core and cultivation to pave the way

53
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,130
for his remnant soul to enter reincarnation.

54
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,400
This ending

55
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,600
is truly tragic.

56
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,140
Wuzhou.

57
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,280
Wuzhou.

58
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,260
Wuzhou,

59
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,120
wake up.

60
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:04,920
Wuzhou.

61
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,280
Wuzhou,

62
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,280
you're awake.

63
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,280
Xiaoxue,

64
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,800
why are you crying?

65
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,840
Does the wound hurt too much?

66
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:21,480
I'm fine.

67
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,010
It doesn't hurt.

68
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,440
How do you feel?

69
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:25,860
I...

70
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:26,880
I'm fine.

71
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:27,970
Don't worry.

72
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,600
Xiaoxue,

73
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,200
please don't cry.

74
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,320
You look pretty when you cry,

75
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,480
but

76
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,280
you look even better when you don't.

77
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,380
At a time like this,

78
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,890
how can you still say things like that?

79
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,300
Is it already over?

80
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:02,290
Look.

81
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,620
It's the flower demon.

82
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,880
Did you defeat the flower demon?

83
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:13,880
I guess

84
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,880
so.

85
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:15,960
Everyone,

86
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,960
your contributions to the people of Nancheng,

87
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:18,880
our Tiandao Palace

88
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:20,280
will surely record them.

89
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,280
No need.

90
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,770
We didn't make much of a contribution.

91
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,160
There is no need to be modest, everyone.

92
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,960
This demon has plagued Nancheng for 30 years.

93
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,620
The duty of our Tiandao Palace

94
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,640
is to protect the peace of the world.

95
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,920
You eliminated the flower demon for us.

96
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,050
We should thank you.

97
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,360
Come.

98
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,680
Present the reward.

99
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,080
Yes.

100
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:44,920
Source Blood.

101
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,730
Why is there a Likong Clan here?

102
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,850
The Likong Clan?

103
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,650
Is it the Likong Clan in the palace?

104
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,720
It is the Likong Clan.

105
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,530
But not the one from the palace.

106
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,320
What should we do now?

107
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,290
Protect her well

108
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,860
and bring her back.

109
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,560
Miss,

110
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,600
please come back with us.

111
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,880
What?

112
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,360
Please, Miss.

113
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,920
Tiandao Palace.

114
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,090
Why did they suddenly start fighting?

115
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,440
Who are you?

116
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:26,440
Why are you interfering with Tiandao Palace's affairs?

117
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:26,920
Well,

118
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,980
I don't want to go with you.

119
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:29,680
Miss.

120
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,440
It's not about whether you want to or not.

121
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,970
Your blood is very special.

122
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,000
You are vulnerable to Ming Demon attacks outside.

123
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,480
We are protecting you.

124
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,760
No, thanks.

125
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,560
I already have someone protecting me.

126
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,320
Being out here,

127
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,380
I'm not afraid of Ming demon attacks.

128
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,600
Miss.

129
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,090
Get lost.

130
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,120
This Likong tribe member

131
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,520
is extremely resistant.

132
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,560
What should we do?

133
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,120
Take her back.

134
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,410
Don't worry about hurting her,

135
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,900
as long as she doesn't die.

136
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,640
Doesn't Tiandao Palace claim to be the justice of the human race?

137
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,160
Yet you are kidnapping me.

138
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,240
Yes.

139
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,280
Someone,

140
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,960
lock it.

141
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,040
Why?

142
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,650
Why did you stand in front of me?

143
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,880
Why was it you?
